This paper discusses short text topic modeling techniques, which are commonly used in natural language processing and information retrieval. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses machine learning algorithms and performance evaluation, which are relevant to sub-categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
